  "page_title": "SMC_CAMBounds_Pos (FB)",
  "text": "\nFUNCTION_BLOCK SMC_CAMBounds_Pos\nIn contrast to\nSMC_CAMBounds\nthis function block calculates only the maximum and minimum position values\nof the slave being coupled in absolute mode to a master which is moved according to a prescribed maximum velocity and acceleration/deceleration.\nThis module is especially helpful when a cam disc is created and modified in online mode and the observance of the maximum values have to be checked in advance.\n",
